Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理讓你輕鬆解壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主角是小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅對抗犯人又暗自煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.37,0:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、小蘭跟叔叔三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一位博士朋友還有他的孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了這個伊豆懸疑之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行團的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主辦人會混在參加者之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.55,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮成暗夜公爵 在旅行中引發一些事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.79,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.01,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揪出主辦者的真實身分除了可以住宿費全免之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.74,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以拿到具有某種程式的磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各懷鬼胎的參加者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮成暗夜公爵的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將落單的我從陽台上面推下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.50,0:02:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來掉進了游泳池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是警告嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這也是遊戲的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後事件發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵竟然從高空掉了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵殺人事件(疑惑篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆公主飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.31,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個戴面具的人掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來的是暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.04,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你好像是和毛利偵探一起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你不能亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是小蘭小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.09,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埼玉警署的橫溝先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是上個月才轉任到靜岡警署的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐你認識這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我們一樣 是懸疑之旅的參加者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懸疑之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼只有戴一隻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.71,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這個旅行團的目的是要揭穿暗夜公爵的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主辦人應該就是這個江原先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自殺還是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 毛利小五郎先生現在在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在二樓的酒吧裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上條小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我就先跟毛利先生談談好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.94,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主飯店二樓翡翠酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒想到爸爸竟然在這種地方喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原先生扮成暗夜公爵的樣子墜樓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據目擊者的證詞指出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他掉到銅像上的時間正好是十點鐘整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這手是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 有酒味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好十點鐘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.68,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你到他住的那間2101號房去調查過了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有 我本來是打算馬上進行調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是進不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他已經從房裡鎖上了防盜鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻把這扇門給我弄開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服竟然丟在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些衣服都是江原先生今天晚上穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連房間鑰匙也丟在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子江原先生一定喝得很醉才會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這窗戶是開著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶外面就是陽臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子江原先生就是從這個地方掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很危險 毛利偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.67,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這只是單純的意外事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的手套還夾在欄杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許是想穿成這個樣子 從陽臺跳下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.16,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇嚇住在樓下房間的參賽者而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到做戲竟然賠上一條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是二十一樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.19,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人會不用繩子從陽臺到樓下去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個房間的鑰匙明明在房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他運氣不錯到了下面的陽臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能從樓下的房間離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個房間的鑰匙還是沒有辦法回到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鋼筆掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.87,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說我們還是去看看屍體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看了 我想結果也是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死得太慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 他是從二十一樓往下掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才插到銅像上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間沒有人靠近屍體嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們警方之外碰過屍體的只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直找都找不到剛才掉下來的那支鋼筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原先生真的掉到樓下死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來的是江原時男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還戴了面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面…面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這次的旅行團的主辦人也就是暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是江原先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始也覺得那個人怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子 不要說這些啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到不死怪人暗夜公爵竟然死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.19,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們這些人到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人都跟我一樣是旅行團的團員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過江原先生為什麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這只是一場意外罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他本來是為了要嚇大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才從陽臺跳下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.89,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 暗夜公爵現在已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個旅行團也就可以結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 這個領帶怎麼會這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點過來看這個領帶結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領帶結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結反了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個領帶結打反了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也許這是他自己的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡有一條他的領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條領帶是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這裡的一個女服務生晚上交給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說是江原先生忘記帶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯 這個領帶的結法跟一般人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又發現什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人的皮帶也好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看繫法也一樣反過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的習慣跟大家都不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾點實在是太不合常理了 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服不是他自己穿上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是某個人幫他穿上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.68,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 江原先生就是被真正的暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從二十一樓的房間推落到銅像上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我就必須詢問各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十點左右江原先生摔下來時候的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.48,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻向飯店借用一個房間當作警方偵訊之用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衣服跟屍體怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們偵訊結束之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先將它們安置在飯店的辦公室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那你在十點的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟小蘭他們在瞭望台那裡欣賞海景了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我跟他們兩個分開的時候剛剛好已經過了十點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說的是真的 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 前田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時看錶的人應該是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫下一個人進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的不在場證明非常完美對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這件事件發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一直跟他待在酒吧裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是叔叔他最後不是醉倒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.11,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時正好就在江原先生被推落到下面的露天餐廳裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 靜江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰能夠證明這一點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.37,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時大家都一陣騷動亂成一團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不知道什麼人還記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人會在那樣的方式下死去也是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從九點四十五分到超過十點鐘的這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在我房裡讀取寄給我的那些電子郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要調查飯店的紀錄應該就會瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這段時間你根本沒有跟誰交談過 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然有交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時妳也一直待在自己的房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰過了十點以後才回房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間我都一個人在看錄影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沒有人能夠證明你的說詞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把那部電影的內容告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在說一個摩天大樓裡面裝置了炸彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種說詞根本不能當證詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人怎麼會這麼倒楣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要一個人看這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望偵訊快點結束就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個刑警跟你爸爸在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定認為我就是那個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸他不會這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外明明還有很多人都很可疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以交班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加旅行團的團員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的說詞都含糊不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你在房間裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有向飯店要什麼客房服務呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有客房服務的話我早就說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手在把江原先生從他房間的陽臺上面推下去之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是用什麼方法逃出房間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間從裡面鎖上了防盜鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要怎麼樣才能逃脫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.94,0:13:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手到目前為止還在這個飯店裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有打電話給櫃檯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有請櫃檯幫我 Morning call
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是十點左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.05,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有使用飯店的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用時間和房間號碼 飯店都會有紀錄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明子小姐就有不在場證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.00,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.07,0:13:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.35,0:14:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 他出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼沒有抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為我嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三澤在遺體安置的房間裡昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子好像是被什麼人打昏的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 遺體呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體倒是沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是暗夜公爵的衣服卻突然不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵在游泳池裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.47,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具和帽子 還有假髮和斗篷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最重要的暗夜公爵人在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那裡沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是從那個陽臺丟下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兇手為什麼會穿成那個樣子出現在電梯前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他要上樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會走避開人的樓梯才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他非要做那樣的打扮不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就沒有必要冒著危險去偷衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種手法太牽強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這次行動在兇手看來是出乎意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們重新進行偵查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在把所有可疑的人員集合起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時大家都在自己房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有人能夠證明這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐山小姐他們在電梯裡遭到攻擊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都沒有不在場證明對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先等一下 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直遵照你的吩咐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在自己的房間裡面 一直沒有出去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還需要證明嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也照你的命令待在房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.58,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可還沒有笨到不把警察看在眼裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳和前田先生在同一個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳有確認他在不在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哪會有這個時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了向警察報告我們遇到暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就下樓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.79,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的房間警方都要檢查一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就從前田先生開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個看來似乎沒有特別可疑之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓新鮮空氣進來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那個臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了謹慎起見 請將口袋裡的東西拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經大概知道這個房間的佈局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原先生就是從那個陽臺掉下來摔死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.11,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是讓江原先生打扮成暗夜公爵的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓整件事看起來像是一件意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.32,0:16:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在凶案現場 也就是江原先生的房間 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻從裡面鎖上了防盜鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說兇手在將江原先生推下樓之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有從他的房門出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這是一件密室殺人案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果兇手能夠從那個房間逃脫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能從陽臺逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他就不可能再從外面進入這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個藥是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是普通的安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近因為有點事失眠所以才放在口袋裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我看看好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我們到下個房間去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.09,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎麼也查不出所以然的 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江原先生是從上面的陽臺被推下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算勉強下來好像也沒有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個臭小子 你怎麼又跟過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想到這裡來學習叔叔做名偵探的樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這麼說的話 那就好好的看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有破壞窗戶的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這個臭小子也有討人喜歡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺 這個窗戶一直是鎖著的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛不好 不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢 靜江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了 每次出去我都會全部檢查一遍 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是去今野先生的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起這個今野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.57,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有人懷疑他擅自使用自己銀行的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說這件事還曝光了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來他也許是我們裡頭最想見到暗夜公爵的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是個謠傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老先生這麼說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還真敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些人裡頭最恨暗夜公爵的人明明就是他自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.23,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.94,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個老頭子自己親手撫養長大的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被那個病毒殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 那個老爺爺這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個名字讓我想起了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.37,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它讓我想起我四年前死去的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的兒子是因為病毒死的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟暗夜公爵有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我就不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙想裝傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們饒了我好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可以告訴你們一個珍貴的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離那個陽臺最近的就是這扇窗戶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他不可能從這裡跳出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上條小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個原本是一對夫妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過他們在三年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次死的江原時男的確是我的前夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那已經是三年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我還不知道他是一個駭客呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.04,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駭客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是擅自盜取電腦資料的惡劣份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是經常使用電腦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都很憎恨駭客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他死了我倒鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得佐山明子小姐的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也開了一家小型的電腦軟體公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 她也就不能免除嫌疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我們這個旅行團的團員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個都有殺害他的動機 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟明子小姐口袋裡的是同一種藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個藥也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 你不要隨便亂碰好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是感冒藥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.74,0:20:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 我還以為是安眠藥 是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.51,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你插什麼嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就快點回房間睡覺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還沒有到那個房間調查過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.07,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定跟樓下的今野先生的房間一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把所有團員的房間配置整理過之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.88,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從江原先生的陽臺逃脫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有經由金城先生跟林小姐的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是防盜鎖的碎片嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 江原先生的房間也在這一層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個前端好像粘著什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是透明膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.93,0:20:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.45,0:22:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他躲開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能夠完全精準地躲開了我的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在所有嫌疑犯裡面可能做到這種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.57,0:22:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了他之外沒有別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴我 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.53,0:22:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.02,0:22:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是鎖上防盜鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.09,0:22:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 我不記得我有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.44,0:22:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試驗成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.68,0:23:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛在打哈欠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.62,0:23:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才的小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.85,0:23:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子應該要睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.61,0:23:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係啦 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.55,0:23:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要利用這個手法 不管是誰都有可能作案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.01,0:23:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還必須一個一個確定大家的不在場證明才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.45,0:23:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你聽說三澤那件事沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是在那個安置遺體的辦公室被人打昏了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.42,0:23:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是三澤他是一個空手道高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 他可是我們局裡段數最高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.06,0:23:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼不小心也不至於昏倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.22,0:23:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.43,0:23:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.54,0:23:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把門鎖上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.00,0:23:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我從外面上鎖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.78,0:23:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 這個房間就形成了密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是假裝成意外的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.71,0:24:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.16,0:24:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.82,0:24:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得有一個地方沒有風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.73,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵殺人事件(解決篇)
