Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.35,0:24:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大廈風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.83,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是解決篇
